020}}</ref> Saibaba Sansthan Trust, [[Shirdi]] donated {{INRConvert|51|c|lk=|year=2020}} to [[Maharashtra]] [[Chief minister (India)|CM]]'s relief fund.<ref>{{cite web |title=Shri Saibaba Sansthan Trust donates Rs 51 cr to combat COVID-19| url=https://www.bignewsnetwork.com/news/264441730/shri-saibaba-sansthan-trust-donates-rs-51-cr-to-combat-covid-19|website=bignewsnetwork|author=| date=27 March 2020|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=27 March 2020}}</ref> The Union Government released {{INRConvert|4431|c|lk=|year=2020}} pay off the pending wages of daily wage laborers who come under MGNREGA scheme.<ref>{{cite web |title=Centre releases Rs 4431 crore to clear pending wages under MGNREGA, to pay all dues by April 10| url=https://m.economictimes.com/news/economy/finance/centre-releases-rs-4431-crore-to-clear-pending-wages-under-mgnrega-to-pay-all-dues-by-april-10/articleshow/74849430.cms|website=Economic Times|author=| date=27 March 2020|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=27 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Centre releases 4,431 crore to clear pending wages under MGNREGA| url=https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/coronavirus-centre-releases-4431-crore-to-clear-pending-wages-under-mgnrega/article31185034.ece/amp/|website=The Hindu|author=| date=27 March 2020|language=en|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=27 March 2020}}</ref> Former [[Bihar]]'s [[Chief minister (India)|CM]] [[Rabri Devi]] donated {{INRConvert|1|c|lk=|year=2020}}.<ref>{{cite web |title=COVID 19: \u0930\u093e\u092c\u0921\u093c\u0940 \u0926\u0947\u0935\u0940 \u0928\u0947 \u0915\u094b\u0930\u094b\u0928\u093e \u0938\u0947 \u0928\u093f\u092a\u091f\u0928\u0947 \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f 1 \u0915\u0930\u094b\u0921\u093c \u0926\u0947\u0928\u0947 \u0915\u093e \u0915\u093f\u092f\u093e \u0910\u0932\u093e\u0928!| url=https://hindi.news18.com/news/bihar/patna-former-cm-and-rjd-leader-rabri-devi-to-donate-rs-one-crore-t