s-and-nation/covid-19-one-indian-in-iran-dead-government-gives-local-help-to-254-others/articleshow/74722021.cms|title=Covid-19: One Indian in Iran dead, Government gives local help to 254 others|date=20 March 2020|work=The Economic Times|access-date=22 March 2020}}</ref> A 3-year-old Indian girl tested positive in Singapore on 26 March, taking total to 277.<ref name=singapore>{{Cite web|url=https://www.timesnownews.com/india/article/3-yr-old-indian-girl-among-73-new-coronavirus-cases-in-singapore-tally-of-infected-people-crosses/569723|title=3-yr-old Indian girl among 73 new coronavirus cases in Singapore, tally of infected people crosses 600|website=www.timesnownews.com|agency=PTI|language=en|access-date=2020-03-26}}</ref>\n{|class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders sortable\" style=\"text-align:right; font-size:90%;\"\n|+\nConfirmed cases of Indian nationals abroad\n!Country/Region\n!Active cases\n!Death\n!Total\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flag|Hong Kong}}\n|1\n|0\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flag|Iran}}\n|254\n|1<ref name=\":1\"/>\n|255\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flag|Italy}}\n|5\n|0\n|5\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flag|Kuwait}}\n|1\n|0\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flag|Rwanda}}\n|1\n|0\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flag|United Arab Emirates}}\n|12\n|0\n|12\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flag|Sri Lanka}}\n|1\n|0\n|1\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"|{{flag|Singapore}}\n|1\n|0\n|1<ref name=singapore/>\n|-\n!Total\n!276\n!1\n!277\n|}\n\n=== States and territories without confirmed cases ===\n\nNo confirmed cases have been reported in the states of [[Arunachal Pradesh]], [[Assam]], [[Jharkhand]], [[Meghalaya]], [[Nagaland]], [[Sikkim]], [[Tripura]] and union territories of [[Dadra and Nagar Haveli and Daman and Diu]] and [[Lakshadweep]].\n\n== See also ==\n*[[Timeline of the 2020 coronavirus pandemic in India]]\n**[[Indian local government response to the 2020 coronavirus pandemic]]\n**[[Economic impact of the 