/150657-eshche-odin-dobrovolec-iz-tomskoi-oblasti-pogib-v-sirii] 14\u201364 killed ([[Battle of Khasham]], Feb. 2018),[https://www.pravda.ru/news/world/1371126-troshev/][https://ssu.gov.ua/en/news/1/category/2/view/5693#.NTRLLcQI.dpbs] 18 killed (May 2018-June 2019),[https://www.yahoo.com/news/26-syria-regime-9-russia-fighters-killed-attack-113110297.html][https://www.themoscowtimes.com/2018/11/06/six-russian-mercenaries-killed-syria-blast-reports-a63403][https://www.uawire.org/russian-officer-killed-in-syria][https://74.ru/text/incidents/66030364/][http://www.syriahr.com/en/?p=125124][https://meduza.io/en/feature/2019/07/29/three-russian-mercenaries-are-killed-in-syria-and-they-re-not-from-the-pmc-you-ve-heard-of] total of 183\u2013283 reported dead</ref>\n|-\n|Other non-Syrian militiamen\n|'''8,067''' killed<ref name=SOHR/>\n|}\n\nThe non-Syrian militiamen fatalities figure includes: over 2,000 [[Liwa Fatemiyoun|Afghans]],<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.middleeasteye.net/news/more-2000-afghans-killed-syria-fighting-bashar-al-assad-official|title=More than 2,000 Afghans killed in Syria fighting for Bashar al-Assad: Official|website=Middle East Eye|accessdate=19 February 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220063140/https://www.middleeasteye.net/news/more-2000-afghans-killed-syria-fighting-bashar-al-assad-official|archive-date=20 February 2019|url-status=live}}<br />[https://en.radiofarda.com/a/khamenei-praises-afghan-refugees-recruited-by-irgc-and-killed-in-syria-war/29850317.html Khamenei Praises Afghans Recruited By IRGC And Killed In Syria War] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330131123/https://en.radiofarda.com/a/khamenei-praises-afghan-refugees-recruited-by-irgc-and-killed-in-syria-war/29850317.html |date=2019-03-30 }}</ref> at least 1,308 [[Iraqi insurgency (Iraq War)#Shia Islamist|Iraqi Shia militiamen]],<ref>2 killed (2012),[https://www.washingtoninstitute.org/uploads/Documents/pubs/PolicyFocus138_Smyth-2.pdf] 1,200 (2013\u2013