712175043/http://www.newyorkupstate.com/buffalo/2017/07/buffalo_area_native_nicholas_warden_killed_battling_isis_in_syria.html |date=2017-07-12 }}[http://www.rudaw.net/english/middleeast/syria/26072017] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730210722/http://www.rudaw.net/english/middleeast/syria/26072017 |date=2017-07-30 }}[https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/isis-syria-war-baghouz-children-us-islamic-state-a8807926.html] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190305120402/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/isis-syria-war-baghouz-children-us-islamic-state-a8807926.html |date=2019-03-05 }}</ref> 50 Swedes,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.thelocal.se/20190224/sweden-debates-fate-of-returned-foreign-fighters|title=Sweden debates fate of returned foreign fighters|accessdate=14 February 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190224104107/https://www.thelocal.se/20190224/sweden-debates-fate-of-returned-foreign-fighters|archive-date=24 February 2019|url-status=live}}</ref> 43 Georgians,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://civil.ge/archives/268733|title=Georgian Citizen Killed in Syria|date=30 November 2018|publisher=|accessdate=19 February 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181130205924/https://civil.ge/archives/268733|archive-date=30 November 2018|url-status=live}}</ref> 39 Dutch,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://nltimes.nl/2017/02/16/prosecute-dutch-jihadists-still-syria-iraq-public-prosecutor|title=PROSECUTE DUTCH JIHADISTS STILL IN SYRIA, IRAQ: PUBLIC PROSECUTOR|accessdate=16 February 2017}}</ref> 37 Italians,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.kurdistan24.net/en/news/4544f7e2-2fa6-42e7-a5a8-f0dcda752269|title=Italian IS fighter captured in Syria by Kurdish-led forces|publisher=kurdistan24.net|date=|accessdate=2018-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180914070453/http://www.kurdistan24.net/en/news/4544f7e2-2fa6-42e7-a5a8-f0dcda752269|archive-date=2018-09-14|url-status=live}}</ref> 36 Malaysians,<ref>{{cit